4717 might be the tip of the iceberg of high-z quasars with\nenhanced X-ray emission, and SRG/eROSITA may find many more such objects during\nits 4 year all-sky survey.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Jul 2020 12:14:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-12"}
